_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1724330347.86390", "card_id": "Q_664929656", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 148}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "借力《黑神话：悟空》，山西旅游热度暴增，这一宝藏古建大省为何才出圈？山西如何才能接住这泼天的流量？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "山西一直被认为是文旅资源宝藏省份，但旅游产业发展的水平和自身资源禀赋并不匹配。据不完全统计，《黑神话：悟空》游戏画面在国内有 36 个取景地，其中 27 个来自山西。游戏上线当天，相关话题登顶社交平台热搜榜单，也让山西文旅迎来一波「泼天的流量」。美团数据显示， 8 月 20 日，《黑神话：悟空》游戏上线当天，山西景区的旅游热度环比增长 156 %，其中云冈石窟、应县木塔、鹳雀楼景区等游戏取景地的旅游热度增幅最高。详见：借力《黑神话：悟空》出圈，山西能否接住这泼天的流量？ - 21 财经"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f8e33e8a91db5b470963fcbe10b3eae3_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664929656"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIs67juOvcjslZEAMaCTExMDAzOTY3MiDut5e2BjAAOKMCQB1yCTY2NDkyOTY1NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}}